snippet.title: How Llamas Will Save Us, Airbnb Wants Your Money, and More Bad Art | Weird News
snippet.description:
📰 In today's funny and weird news, we will learn about the medical properties of llamas, that Airbnb wants you to donate to a landlord, and that bad art is everywhere. Also, what a peacock sounds like.
👍 Please like and subscribe if you enjoyed!

What to expect
------------------
00:00 — reflection on recent Kentucky adventures
00:10 — preview of what we'll look at today
01:27 — what a peacock sounds like and why Nextdoor is fighting about it
03:07 — why Airbnb wants us to donate to landlords
03:37 — why Placerville has a noose in its logo
04:57 — how often Amazon employees wash their hands
05:21 — how perfumes are being made by those who can't smell
05:52 — banksy makes some new art
06:02 — celebrity battle: Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard
06:28 — headlines we don't need to click on to understand
07:16 — old people recreate classic album covers
08:18 — some bad art gets donated to a school
08:57 — the medical properties of llamas

------------------

Background music: Thru The Wall by Matt Large
Outro music: Eastern Shades by Matt Large
